summary: This adds a beautiful little forest and Underground house into land of Skyrim.
descriptionHtml:
ONLY HOUSE IS UNDERGROUND, THE FOREST AND NESTS WITH PRESENTS ARE NOT.

This is a mod with a nice player house that contains everything you need, yes a forge, a tanning rack, Workbench, Grindstone, Enchanter, Alchemy table.
And there are mannequins, bedroom, OK, That\'s enough, but there are a lot of things I did not mention about this mod. And important thing you should know about this mod is that there are NESTS ! Yeah bird nests, but these are special they have all kinds of stuff around or in them so watch for the nests :)

                                                 ENJOY ! :-)

-1.1v - fixed light flashing and added a little garden in crafting section.-

1.2v - Added more trees and nests ,of course and more presents in nests are added and two shrine of Talos, entrance is not in the rock anymore, I added a tent !

1.3v 
-Most of the things are fixed 
-There is a special room (Doors to the room are in the Underground house bedroom)
-Big forest area named Wonder world (Doors to the room are in the Underground house bedroom)

1.4v
-So now The wonder world name is changed 
-The entry is not in a tent anymore I added a house (IT IS NOT THE ORIGINAL UNDERGROUND HOUSE) and the Entry to your Underground home is in that house
-So this is the last update hope you enjoy it !

Please view the images section for location and to see some parts of house !

If you like it endorse If It Is Not A Big Problem . :)  And Vote Of Course.
author: Marky123
